00:15:49.988 --> 00:15:54.426
Because those lines
are you talking.

00:15:54.838 --> 00:15:55.936
Now this time,

00:15:56.872 --> 00:15:59.400
take two characters
that are not you

00:16:01.615 --> 00:16:03.657
but have the same dilemma.

00:16:04.113 --> 00:16:05.589
- Only one object?

00:16:05.906 --> 00:16:07.870
Just one first.

00:16:08.884 --> 00:16:11.439
- Do you want more?
- No, not really.

00:16:11.464 --> 00:16:13.035
- But what if something new shows up?

00:16:13.815 --> 00:16:14.861
That's fine, too.

00:16:16.116 --> 00:16:18.843
It's okay.
A set of objects, if you want.

00:16:19.897 --> 00:16:20.897
A list.

00:16:23.052 --> 00:16:25.397
I'm really only giving you five minutes.

00:16:25.573 --> 00:16:26.792
- That's harder.

00:16:28.108 --> 00:16:30.188
When I finish this game,

00:16:31.141 --> 00:16:32.195
your time's up.
